  "detailed_description": "<h1>YOU MAY ALSO LIKE</h1><p><br><br></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Come back into the tranquil beauty of nature with Nature Escapes 2, the latest chapter in the beloved hidden object game series. Explore over 30 peaceful chapters filled with stunning landscapes and soothing gameplay, all set to relaxing music that enhances your experience.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221630/extras/2750c0ca950a608cd26936fe303a5461.poster.avif?t=1723445324\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221630/extras/2750c0ca950a608cd26936fe303a5461.webm?t=1723445324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221630/extras/2750c0ca950a608cd26936fe303a5461.mp4?t=1723445324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Discover hidden treasures in a variety of serene settings and create your own garden sanctuary with an expanded selection of plants and decorations. With more levels, more plants, and more soothing scenes, Nature Escapes 2 offers the perfect escape into nature’s calm.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore 20+ relaxing chapters of hidden object scenes and minigames.<br></li><li>Discover over 70 hidden object scenes and minigames.<br></li><li>Enjoy gentle, calming music as you play.<br></li><li>Expand and decorate your garden with new plants and flowers.<br></li><li>Discover beautiful, handcrafted nature scenes from around the world.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221630/extras/f7218a17e97cec821145f0e7e964c397.poster.avif?t=1723445324\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221630/extras/f7218a17e97cec821145f0e7e964c397.webm?t=1723445324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221630/extras/f7218a17e97cec821145f0e7e964c397.mp4?t=1723445324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Experience the calming beauty of nature with Nature Escapes 2, and create your dream garden in a peaceful, immersive game.",
  "about_the_game": "Come back into the tranquil beauty of nature with Nature Escapes 2, the latest chapter in the beloved hidden object game series. Explore over 30 peaceful chapters filled with stunning landscapes and soothing gameplay, all set to relaxing music that enhances your experience.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221630/extras/2750c0ca950a608cd26936fe303a5461.poster.avif?t=1723445324\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221630/extras/2750c0ca950a608cd26936fe303a5461.webm?t=1723445324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221630/extras/2750c0ca950a608cd26936fe303a5461.mp4?t=1723445324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Discover hidden treasures in a variety of serene settings and create your own garden sanctuary with an expanded selection of plants and decorations. With more levels, more plants, and more soothing scenes, Nature Escapes 2 offers the perfect escape into nature’s calm.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore 20+ relaxing chapters of hidden object scenes and minigames.<br></li><li>Discover over 70 hidden object scenes and minigames.<br></li><li>Enjoy gentle, calming music as you play.<br></li><li>Expand and decorate your garden with new plants and flowers.<br></li><li>Discover beautiful, handcrafted nature scenes from around the world.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221630/extras/f7218a17e97cec821145f0e7e964c397.poster.avif?t=1723445324\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221630/extras/f7218a17e97cec821145f0e7e964c397.webm?t=1723445324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221630/extras/f7218a17e97cec821145f0e7e964c397.mp4?t=1723445324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Experience the calming beauty of nature with Nature Escapes 2, and create your dream garden in a peaceful, immersive game.",
